(1550, 1, '2019-04-29 07:06:37', '2019-04-29 07:06:37', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">More about the project</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">KSR Basil in Budigere Cross, Bangalore East by KSR Properties is a residential project.\r\nThe project offers Apartment with perfect combination of contemporary architecture and features to provide comfortable living.\r\n\r\nThe Apartment are of the following configurations: 1BHK, 2BHK and 3BHK\r\n\r\nThe size of the Apartment ranges in between 611.0 sq.ft. and 1722.0 sq.ft.\r\n\r\nKSR Basil price ranges from 21.99 Lacs to 61.99 Lacs.\r\n\r\nKSR Basil offers facilities such as Gymnasium and Lift.\r\nIt also has amenities like Badminton court, Basketball court, Jogging track and Swimming pool.\r\nIt also offers services like Library.\r\n\r\nIt also offers Car parking.\r\n\r\nThe project is Vastu complaint.\r\n\r\nThis is a RERA registered project with registration number PRM/KA/RERA/1251/446/PR/180519/001744.\r\n\r\nBank loan approved from HDFC home loans, State Bank of India, Punjab National Bank, AXIS Bank LTD., LIC Housing Finance Ltd., Indiabulls and DHFL Vysya Housing Finance Limited.\r\n\r\nIt is an under construction project with possession offered in Dec, 2019.\r\n\r\nThe project is spread over a total area of 5.5 acres of land. It has 40% of open space.\r\nKSR Basil has a total of 11 towers. The construction is of 4 floors. An accommodation of 332 units has been provided.\r\n\r\nAbout City:\r\n\r\nBangalore is growing in every aspect. The major growth drivers of the city is the booming IT sector that is generating numerous jobs. This has also impacted the real estate market of the city very positively. The city with multi-cultural population and good social infrastructure, excellent educational institutes and constantly upgrading physical infrastructure, witnesses a positive trend in its real estate market.\r\nThe city has a wide mix of luxury ho