(1452, 1, '2019-04-28 07:17:50', '2019-04-28 07:17:50', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">More about the project</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">Adarsh Citrine in 7th Phase JP Nagar, Bangalore South by Adarsh Developers is a residential project.\r\nThe project offers Apartment with perfect combination of contemporary architecture and features to provide comfortable living.\r\n\r\nThe Apartment are of the following configurations: 2BHK and 3BHK\r\n\r\nThe size of the Apartment ranges in between 1335.0 sq.ft. and 2225.0 sq.ft.\r\n\r\nAdarsh Citrine offers facilities such as Gymnasium and Lift.\r\nIt also offers services like Community hall.\r\n\r\nIt also offers Car parking.\r\n\r\nThis is a RERA registered project with registration number PRM/KA/RERA/1251/310/PR/170915/000332.\r\n\r\nBank loan approved from State Bank of India.\r\n\r\nIt is a ready to move project with possession offered in Aug, 2018.\r\n\r\nThe project is spread over a total area of 1.4 acres of land. It has 51% of open space.\r\nAdarsh Citrine has a total of 4 towers. The construction is of 4 floors. An accommodation of 64 units has been provided.\r\n\r\nAdarsh Citrine brochure is also available for easy reference.\r\n\r\nAbout City:\r\n\r\nBangalore is growing in every aspect. The major growth drivers of the city is the booming IT sector that is generating numerous jobs. This has also impacted the real estate market of the city very positively. The city with multi-cultural population and good social infrastructure, excellent educational institutes and constantly upgrading physical infrastructure, witnesses a positive trend in its real estate market.\r\nThe city has a wide mix of luxury housing, mid segment housing and affordable housing.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">1.40 Acres (51%)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">4 Towers64 Units 4 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 2, 3 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"npMainHeading\">7th Phase JP Nagar Highlights</div>\r\n<p class=\"npText\">7th Phase JP Nagar is an established residential locality in the southern zone of Bangalore. Apart from shopping malls and entertainment outlets, 7th Phase JP Nagar has a number of reputed public schools, colleges, multi-specialty hospitals in the close vicinity. Further, the locality enjoys seamless connectivity with other parts of the city through the network of highways and roadways. As a result of these positive factors, the locality has become a favorable destination to invest and reside in.</p>\r\n<p class=\"npText\">Electronic City Flyover is at a drive of 30 minutes from this area.</p>\r\nFor more details please contact us.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"xid_descInnerWrapper\" class=\"contentInnerWrap floatf\">\r\n<div class=\"social99 contentInnerWrapIn\"></div>\r\n</div>', 'Live Better at  Adarsh Citrine', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'live-better-at-adarsh-citrine', '', '', '2019-04-28 07:17:50', '2019-04-28 07:17:50', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1452', 0, 'property', '', 0),
