(1102, 1, '2019-04-17 07:13:42', '2019-04-17 07:13:42', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">More about the project</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">Keerthi Royal Palms in Lavakusha Nagar, Bangalore South by Keerthi Estates Builders is a residential project.\r\nThe project offers Apartment with perfect combination of contemporary architecture and features to provide comfortable living.\r\n\r\nThe Apartment are of the following configurations: 2BHK and 3BHK</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"prjctDesc\">Keerthi Royal Palms price ranges from 55.00 Lacs to 90.00 Lacs\r\n\r\nKeerthi Royal Palms offers facilities such as Gymnasium and Lift.\r\nIt also has amenities like Basketball court, Jogging track, Lawn tennis court and Swimming pool.\r\nIt also offers Car parking.\r\n\r\nThis is a RERA registered project with registration number PRM/KA/RERA/1251/310/PR/171031/001598.\r\n\r\nBank loan approved from HDFC home loans, ICICI, Punjab National Bank, LIC Housing Finance Ltd. and PNB Housing Finance Limited.\r\n\r\nIt is a ready to move project with possession offered in Mar, 2019.\r\n\r\nThe project is spread over a total area of 7 acres of land. It has 65% of open space.\r\nKeerthi Royal Palms has a total of 5 towers. The construction is of 12 floors. An accommodation of 381 units has been provided.\r\n\r\n\r\nAbout City:\r\n\r\nBangalore is growing in every aspect. The major growth drivers of the city is the booming IT sector that is generating numerous jobs. This has also impacted the real estate market of the city very positively. The city with multi-cultural population and good social infrastructure, excellent educational institutes and constantly upgrading physical infrastructure, witnesses a positive trend in its real estate market.\r\nThe city has a wide mix of luxury housing, mid segment housing and affordable housing.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">7.00 Acres (65%)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">5 Towers381 Units 12 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 2, 3 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2BHK appartments available for sale with good connectivity, Keerthi Royal Palms', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '2bhk-appartments-available-for-sale-with-good-connectivity-keerthi-royal-palms', '', '', '2019-04-17 07:13:42', '2019-04-17 07:13:42', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1102', 0, 'property', '', 0),
