(1300, 1, '2019-04-25 05:57:04', '2019-04-25 05:57:04', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">Vertical Oriana is the new sublime creation of residential cum commercial property by Vertical Infra in the Pune. These well-designed homes are located in the prime location Mundhwa, Pune. The project offers 2BHK, 3BHK apartments and 4BHK town-houses and penthouses with adjoining servant quarters at affordable pricing that are well equipped with all the latest facilities and amenities. The project is a great choice for the buyers as it is a perfect blend of beauty and modern amenities and proximity to several prestigious gated communities, schools and shopping malls. So, grab this opportunity and book your apartment today.</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">\r\nArchitect: Group Phi Architects and Designers\r\n\r\nFEATURES\r\nPre-certified 4-star Griha project\r\nPerformance stage and cultural enclave\r\nPalms with hammock swing\r\nSky deck\r\nPick up and drop point\r\nCascading welcome foundation\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">3.07 Acres (40%)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">3 Towers222 Units 17 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 2, 3 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class=\"npMainHeading\">Keshav Nagar Highlights</div>\r\n<p class=\"npText\">Keshav Nagar is an emerging location in Mundhwa. It has many upcoming housing projects that offer spaciously designed 2BHK, 3BHK and 4BHK units in Pune. Keshav Nagar connects to the rest of the city via Magarpatta main Road and Ghopardi Road. Pune Airport is located at a short drive of 20 mins.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Experience the Vertical Oriana  Lifestyle.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'experience-the-vertical-oriana-lifestyle', '