(1123, 1, '2019-04-17 09:09:48', '2019-04-17 09:09:48', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">More about the project</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">\r\n\r\nBrigade Buena Vista is a residential development by Brigade Developers which is located in Budigere, Bangalore. It offers 2BHK, 2.5BHK and 3BHK apartments that are available at affordable price and furnished with outstanding amenities.\r\n\r\nPROJECT DETAILS\r\nNumber of floors: 2 Basement + Ground + 22 floors\r\n\r\nFEATURES\r\nPalm vista\r\nEsplanade garden\r\nSocial corner\r\nSand pit\r\nBotanic garden\r\nStepped seating\r\nBamboo garden\r\n\r\nABOUT LOCALITY\r\nBudigere is a small locality situated near Devanhalli, at the northern part of Bangalore. It is a highly developing area with huge number of residential localities as the renowned builders are launching many new projects. Several top IT companies are choosing it as their operational hub due to which the demand for affordable housing and rental property has increased. The nearest railway station is Devanhalli station, which is located at a distance of around 17.8 Km whereas Bangalore International Airport measures around 17 Km.\r\n\r\nABOUT CITY\r\nBangalore, a prominent IT/ITes hub of South India is touching new horizon in terms of realty expansion. It has attracted big number of workforce that has led to massive housing needs. The city is more focused on MIG properties due to large number of mid-level IT professionals. According to recent reports, the new housing demand for urban societies in India is expected to reach nearly 13 million by 2018. With improved infrastructure, excellent transportation and world-class civic amenities, people across India is opting Bangalore for the property investments.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">7.00 Acres (80%)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">4 Towers742 Units 22 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 1, 2, 3, 4 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2BHK new appartment for sale in Brigade Buena Vista', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '2bhk-new-appartment-for-sale-in-brigade-buena-vista', '', '', '2019-04-17 09:11:11', '2019-04-17 09:11:11', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1123', 0, 'property', '', 0),
