(1184, 1, '2019-04-19 10:41:24', '2019-04-19 10:41:24', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">More about the project</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">\r\n\r\nTheme Ambience Golf View is a residential project by Theme Ambience Constructions. It is located in Hyderabad. It offers 2BHK and 3BHK apartments with all basic amenities to facilitate the need of residents.\r\n\r\nAPPROVALS: HUDA/GHMC\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">4.00 Acres (70%)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">5 Towers378 Units 15 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 2, 3 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"npMainHeading\">Nanakramguda Highlights</div>\r\n<p class=\"npText\">Strategically located along the Nehru Outer Ring Road, Nanakramguda is a residential locality of Hyderabad. It enjoys proximity to the major IT suburb; Gachibowli. With an influx of people from different parts of the city, the locality has witnessed an increase in the demand for residential properties.</p>\r\nFor more details please contact us.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Newly Renovated With Amazing Natural Light', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'newly-renovated-with-amazing-natural-light', '', '', '2019-04-19 10:41:37', '2019-04-19 10:41:37', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1184', 0, 'property', '', 0),
