(1427, 1, '2019-04-27 10:55:55', '2019-04-27 10:55:55', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">More about the project</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">Arvind Sporcia in Hebbal, Bangalore North by Arvind Smartspaces is a residential project.\r\nHighlights of project:\r\nICC Standard Size 22 Yard Cricket Pitch.\r\nInternational Tennis Federation Approved Court.\r\n\r\nThe project offers Apartment with perfect combination of contemporary architecture and features to provide comfortable living.\r\n\r\nThe Apartment are of the following configurations: 2BHK and 3BHK\r\n\r\nArvind Sporcia price ranges from 62.99 Lacs to 66.68 Lacs.\r\n\r\nArvind Sporcia offers facilities such as Gymnasium and Lift.\r\nIt also has amenities like Basketball court, Jogging track, Lawn tennis court and Swimming pool.\r\nThe project has indoor activities such as Dart board, Pool table, Skating rink and Squash court.\r\nIt also offers services like Grocery shop.\r\n\r\nIt also offers Car parking.\r\n\r\nThis is a RERA registered project with registration number PRM/KA/RERA/1251/309/PR/171010/000768.\r\n\r\nBank loan approved from HDFC home loans, ICICI, IDBI Bank Ltd., Yes Bank, AXIS Bank LTD. and LIC Housing Finance Ltd.\r\n\r\nIt is a ready to move project.\r\n\r\nThe project is spread over a total area of 4.92 acres of land. Arvind Sporcia has a total of 7 towers. The construction is of 14 floors. An accommodation of 456 units has been provided.\r\n\r\n\r\nAbout City:\r\n\r\nThe front-runner in south India\'s property market, Bangalore is the IT capital of India. It witnesses increasing demands from ITES sector and start-ups professionals. Other factors that contribute to the positive real estate market of the city are positive buyer sentiments, increased commercial activities and an optimistic job market. Additionally, the presence of excellent education and healthcare facilities in the city contribute to the growing realty market.\r\nFrom affordable housing to luxury housing solutions, the city offers a number of residential and commercial projects to investors and buyers.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">4.92 Acres</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">7 Towers456 Units 14 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 2, 3 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nFor more details please contact us.</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"xid_descInnerWrapper\" class=\"contentInnerWrap floatf\">\r\n<div class=\"social99 contentInnerWrapIn\"></div>\r\n</div>', 'Location, Community, Quality Living. It Starts Here!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'location-community-quality-living-it-starts-here', '', '', '2019-04-27 10:55:55', '2019-04-27 10:55:55', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1427', 0, 'property', '', 0),
(1197, 1, '2019-04-19 12:25:32', '2019-04-19 12:25:32', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\"></h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">Sikhara Bliss is one of the residential developments by Sikhara Projects and Infra, located in Hyderabad. The project offers 2BHK, 3BHK and 4BHK flats at very competitive and affordable price. It is well planned and is built with all modern amenities.\r\n\r\nPROJECT DETAILS\r\nLegal Approval: GHMC\r\nBank Approval: All leading banks\r\n\r\nFEATURES\r\nCar wash area\r\nBlack top roads\r\nIndoor games area\r\nDesigner street lamps\r\nCorporation bore well\r\nGood cross ventilation\r\nThree phase electricity\r\nPlantation and proper landscaping\r\n100% clear tile/immediate registration\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">2.00 Acres (30%)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">1 Towers156 Units 6 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 2, 3, 4 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"npMainHeading\">Attapur Highlights</div>\r\n<p class=\"npText\">Attapur is a prominent residential and commercial locale in Hyderabad and sub-divided into many sub-localities. The P.V. Narasimha Rao Expressway passing across the area provides connectivity to the main city. Many important government offices like NACIN has its Zonal Training Institute, sub-divisional Magistrate and Revenue division Office, RTO are located here. The locality is famous for its recreational avenues. The Himayat Sagar reservoir is in close proximity to Attapur. The Retail Corporate giants Walmart and Metro Cash and Carry are close to Attapur. The area is very well developed and boasts to have many prominent University campuses in its vicinity.</p>\r\nFor more details please contact us.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"xid_descInnerWrapper\" class=\"contentInnerWrap floatf\">\r\n<div class=\"social99 contentInnerWrapIn\"></div>\r\n</div>', 'Love this building! Love this location! Amazing Stuff in Cool Area', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'love-this-building-love-this-location-amazing-stuff-in-cool-area', '', '', '2019-04-19 12:25:32', '2019-04-19 12:25:32', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1197', 0, 'property', '', 0),
