(1210, 1, '2019-04-20 09:36:41', '2019-04-20 09:36:41', '<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">\r\n\r\nVaishnavi Oasis, located in Hyderabad, is a residential development of Vaishnavi Infracon. It offers spacious and skillfully designed 2BHK, 3BHK and 4BHK apartments. The project is well equipped with all the basic amenities to facilitate the needs of the residents. The site is in close proximity to various civic utilities.\r\n\r\nArchitect: Aslam architect and interior designers\r\n\r\nLegal Approval: HMDA\r\n\r\nFeatures\r\n3 Layer Security System\r\nCentralized internet\r\nVermicompost for Kitchen Waste Treatment\r\nSolar panels\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">3.00 Acres</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">6 Towers336 Units 9 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 2, 3, 4 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"npMainHeading\">Appa Junction Highlights</div>\r\n<p class=\"npText\">Appa Junction is one of the most promising localities in Hyderabad. The locale is developing rapidly and witnessing a great improvement which promises a positive return in future. Many prominent builders are coming up with top-notch residential projects in this region. The area has adequate schools, hospitals and markets. Attracting both home seekers and developers, it is a good investment destination.</p>\r\nFor more details please contact us.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"xid_descInnerWrapper\" class=\"contentInnerWrap floatf\">\r\n<div class=\"social99 contentInnerWrapIn\"></div>\r\n</div>', 'A Better Quality of Living', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'a-better-quality-of-living', '', '', '2019-04-20 09:39:26', '2019-04-20 09:39:26', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?po