(1233, 1, '2019-04-21 09:36:04', '2019-04-21 09:36:04', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">More about the project</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">\r\n\r\nSiri Vijaya Enclave is a popular residential development in Nagole, Hyderabad. Developed by Siri Constructions, this project offers 2BHK and 3BHK villas with basic amenities for the comfort of residents. It is close to many educational institutions.\r\n\r\nProject Details\r\nNumber of Floors: G+1\r\nNumber of Units: 63\r\nLegal Approvals: GHMC Approved\r\n\r\nProximities\r\n2.5 km from Nagole X road &amp; Metro Station\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">63 Units 2 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Villa | 2, 3 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"npMainHeading\">Nagole Highlights</div>\r\n<p class=\"npText\">Nagole is one of the residential localities of Hyderabad. It is well-connected by different public transit systems and has all the daily essentials situated in close proximity. Further, this area has witnessed growth in real estate with the real estate boom and has emerged to be a very preferred location for potential home buyers. Several new apartments and independent houses are being built by many real estate developers to cater to this demand.</p>\r\nFor more details please contact us.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"xid_descInnerWrapper\" class=\"contentInnerWrap floatf\">\r\n<div class=\"social99 contentInnerWrapIn\"></div>\r\n</div>', 'Life Just Got Better.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'life-just-got-better', '', '', '2019-04-21 09:38:41', '2019-04-21 09:38:41', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1233', 0, 'property', '', 0),
