(1236, 1, '2019-04-21 11:17:28', '2019-04-21 11:17:28', '<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"project-desc-wrap\">\r\n<p class=\"proj-desc full-desc js-more-less-parent js-long-overview-link\" data-display-selector=\".js-short-overview-link\">Jain Housing Salzburg is developing an up to date residential project in Kismatpur region of Hyderabad. The entire project is delivering a range of well-planned and well-designed apartments. The size of the apartments and further details can be availed on request. All the necessary requirements of daily life like bus station, hospital, bank, commercial complex, ATM, office headquarters, petrol pump, train station etc all are present in the neighbourhood. The different amenities of the project are eco-friendly green environment, playground, wide road, childrens school, 24 hours water supply, intercom services, religious places and much more. The cost of the apartments is depended on the request value.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"npMainHeading\">Bandlaguda Highlights</div>\r\n<p class=\"npText\">Being part of HMDA and well connected by rail and road network, Bandlaguda has become one of the prime residential locale of the city of Hyderabad. It is one of the sough-after locality for the working professionals due to its proximity to the corporate establishments and offices. The area has witnessed the advent of several ventures which has escalated its real estate value. It is one of the largest region under Gandipet Mandal. very close to picturesque Himayat Sagar and Osman Sagar fresh water lakes and famous National Park – Mrugavani National Park which covers an area of about 700 acres. Rivers Esi And Musi also flow close by. Bandlaguda is further divided into many sub-localities.</p>\r\nFor more details please contact us.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"app-banks fade-in\" data-module-type=\"banklist\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Love Where You Live! 2', ''