(1266, 1, '2019-04-23 09:27:40', '2019-04-23 09:27:40', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\"> Favolosa is a residential cum commercial projects of Abhilasha Developers and Neel Group. It is located at Balewadi, Pune. The project offers an option of 2BHK and 3BHK apartments as well as shops. It offers spacious homes with congestion free amenities. The site is well equipped with modern day amenities and facilitates all major needs of its residents. The site is well connected by different modes of transportation and is in close proximity of various civic utilities.</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">\r\nPROJECT DETAILS\r\nArchitect Name: Prakash Kanekar and Associates\r\nBank Approval: Piramal Housing\r\nIndia Infoline\r\n\r\nFEATURES\r\nRelaxation benches\r\nRamps for handicap friendliness\r\n\r\nLOCATION HIGHLIGHTS\r\nBalewadi is a suburban locality in North West Pune that has connectivity to Hinjewadi via Balewadi through Katraj - Dehu Road corridor. Balewadi has created its name in Indore\'s property market for offering luxury standard living space to the huge crowd of comfort seeking professionals who work in and around the vicinity. There is more to the luxury giving and well-developed infrastructure.\r\n\r\nConnectivity:\r\nNh-48 (10 min) | Pune railway station (20 min)\r\n\r\nNearby:\r\nSchools: CM International School | Indira National School | Euro kids\r\nHospitals: Sanjeevni Hospital | Polaris Healthcare\r\nInstitutes: MITCON Institute of Management | Mediplus Speciality Hospital | Pune university\r\n\r\n(Distances are straight line measurements from center of the locality.)\r\n\r\nABOUT CITY\r\nPune\'s real estate market has been on a rise with the organized realty landscape and world-class construction. A strategically located city with a beautiful weather all year long, Pune is among the most sought after cities for realty investments. This demand is due to some of the influencing factors including swift connectivity, ferrous infrastructure, availability of reputed companies, upgraded civic utilities and improved socio -economic conditions. These ongoing developments have gained the attention of both potential homebuyers and developers to invest in the city\'s real estate sector.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">1.62 Acres (10%)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">2 Towers79 Units 11 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 2, 3 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nFor more details please contact us.</div>\r\n</div>', 'New with a View', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'new-with-a-view', '', '', '2019-04-23 09:27:40', '2019-04-23 09:27:40', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1266', 0, 'property', '', 0),
