(1371, 1, '2019-04-26 06:20:39', '2019-04-26 06:20:39', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">More about the project</h3>\r\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\r\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">Arge Helios in Narayanapura, Bangalore East by Arge Realty is a residential project.\r\nHighlights of project:\r\nTemperature Controlled Infinity Sky Pool.\r\nBusiness Centre and Private Screening Room.\r\n\r\nThe project offers Apartment with perfect combination of contemporary architecture and features to provide comfortable living.\r\n\r\nThe Apartment are of the following configurations: 2BHK, 3BHK, 4BHK and 5BHK\r\n\r\nThe size of the Apartment ranges in between 1308.0 sq.ft. and 3626.0 sq.ft.\r\n\r\nArge Helios price ranges from 90.00 Lacs to 1.00 Cr.\r\n\r\nArge Helios offers facilities such as Gymnasium and Lift.\r\nIt also has amenities like Basketball court and Swimming pool.\r\nThe project has indoor activities such as Squash court.\r\nIt also offers services like Banquet hall and Library.\r\n\r\nIt also offers Car parking.\r\n\r\nThe project is Vastu complaint.\r\n\r\nBank loan approved from ICICI.\r\n\r\nIt is a ready to move project with possession offered in Mar, 2016.\r\n\r\nThe project is spread over a total area of 2 acres of land. It has 80% of open space.\r\nArge Helios has a total of 1 towers. The construction is of 14 floors. An accommodation of 151 units has been provided.\r\n\r\nYou can find Arge Helios price list on 99acres.com\r\nArge Helios brochure is also available for easy reference.\r\n\r\nAbout City:\r\n\r\nThe front-runner in south India\'s property market, Bangalore is the IT capital of India. It witnesses increasing demands from ITES sector and start-ups professionals. Other factors that contribute to the positive real estate market of the city are positive buyer sentiments, increased commercial activities and an optimistic job market. Additionally, the presence of excellent education and healthcare facilities in the city contribute to the growing realty market.\r\nFrom affordable housing to luxury housing solutions, the city offers a number of residential and commercial projects to investors and buyers.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">2.00 Acres (80%)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">1 Towers151 Units 14 Floors</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\r\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 2, 3, 4, 5 BHK</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nFor more details please contact us.</div>\r\n</div>', 'At Last, This Is What You’ve Been Searching For.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'at-last-this-is-what-youve-been-searching-for', '', '', '2019-04-26 06:20:39', '2019-04-26 06:20:39', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1371', 0, 'property', '', 0),
