(1407, 1, '2019-04-27 06:07:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<h3 class=\"npMainHeading\">More about the project</h3>\n<div id=\"descriptionSection\" class=\"clr333 textL\">\n<div id=\"item_desc\" class=\"prjctDesc\">Salarpuria Sattva East Crest is a thoughtfully designed project by Salarpuria Sattva Group located at Old Madras Road, East Bangalore. The project offers 1BHK, 2BHK and 3BHK apartments suiting the requirements of the modern age home buyers and is Karnataka RERA registered.\n\nAPPROVAL\nThe Bruhat Bengaluru Mahanagara Palike\n\nABOUT LOCALITY\nOld Madras Road (OMR) (National Highway No 4) is a coveted and premium neighborhood of Bangalore, which has rapidly transformed itself into a cosmopolitan center of the city, boasting a number of residential as well as commercial options. A boost in the civic infrastructure and the resultant fast-tracked development have added to the realty market here. OMR is also the entry point to Whitefield, the IT hub of the city. Also the signal-free corridor of the Outer Ring Road (ORR) is the main reason for the increased investments here in OMR. Some other location advantages offered by OMR include:\nProposed train route which will decongest OMR and the nearby locations.\nProximity to IT hubs and important commercial centers of the city.\nUpcoming metro network.\n\nABOUT CITY\nRealty segment of Bangalore has matured remarkably over past few years. Ranging from affordable to luxury properties, the market is a broader one with a steady demand coming up from the buyers a well as investors, in both residential and commercial segments. However, as per the market watchers, residential property has brought about good news for the developers. There has been extensive demands for value homes or mid-segment homes in Bangalore, and they are vaster as compared to the supply.\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"wd150\">Total Project Area:</th>\n<td class=\"f14\">6.77 Acres (62%)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"wd150\">Project Details:</th>\n<td class=\"f14\">11 Towers667 Units 17 Floors</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"wd150\">Configurations:</th>\n<td class=\"f14\">Apartment | 1, 2, 3 BHK</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\nFor more details please contact us.</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n<div id=\"xid_descInnerWrapper\" class=\"contentInnerWrap floatf\">\n<div class=\"social99 contentInnerWrapIn\"></div>\n</div>', 'Beauty, Passion, Breathtaking Apartments! 2', '', 'draft', 'open', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2019-04-27 06:07:59', '2019-04-27 06:07:59', '', 0, 'http://5ineprojects.com/downtown/?post_type=property&#038;p=1407', 0, 'property', '', 0),
